      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in pristine shape inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Send me a message, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
