    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the mechanical integrity is superlative. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014addressing the critical structural weak points of the chassis. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain delivers linear power and exceptional tactile feedback. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather shows no bolster wear. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a concours-ready vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Mint condition. No cosmetic or mechanical defects. Garage kept. Service records available. Cash or certified check only.",
      "price": 43500.0,
