    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Every inch of the deep, lustrous paint has been meticulously preserved, free of swirls or imperfections, and protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the leather is supple and fragrant, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at certified dealerships with a full binder of records to prove its pampered life. It starts, shifts, and handles exactly as it did the day it was delivered. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a spotless history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
